properties.Regular Expression: double\W| float\W| int\W| smallint\W| string\W| timestamp\W| tinyint\W| varchar[\(\d\),]+\W| bigint\W| boolean\W| char[\(\d\),]+\W| date\W| decimal[\(\d\),]+\W

properties.hive-query:
SELECT d.name, t.tbl_name, c.column_name, c.type_name 
 FROM sys.sds s, sys.columns_v2 c, sys.tbls t, sys.dbs d 
 WHERE s.cd_id = c.cd_id AND t.sd_id = s.sd_id 
 AND t.tbl_name = "#{table}"  
 AND t.db_id = d.db_id 
 AND d.name = "#{database}"

parameters.description: The hive database that will contain the temporary tables created from the discovered file.
parameters.name: tmpdb

parameters.description: What database is the table in?
parameters.name: database

parameters.description: Should the file be deleted upon successful insert
parameters.name: deleteOnSuccess

parameters.description: What table will the data be inserted into?
parameters.name: table
